{
  "meta": {
    "eyebrow": "A2 · Propuestas y permisos",
    "title": "Propuestas y",
    "titleEmphasis": "permisos"
  },
  "cards": [
    {
      "id": "pp-suggest",
      "tag": "Sugerir",
      "title": "Let's y Why don't we",
      "lede": "Para proponer hacer algo juntos. Ambas usan el verbo base.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "rules",
          "rows": [
            { "key": "Let's", "value": "Let's go! · Let's eat.", "highlights": ["Let's"] },
            { "key": "Why don't we", "value": "Why don't we watch a movie?", "highlights": ["Why don't we"] },
            { "key": "How about", "value": "How about pizza? · How about going out?", "highlights": ["How about"] }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tip": {
        "label": "Ojo:",
        "body": "tras How about va -ing o un sustantivo: How about going, no \"How about go\"."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "pp-shall",
      "tag": "Ofrecer",
      "title": "Shall I...? / Can I help?",
      "lede": "Para ofrecer ayuda o hacer algo por alguien. Shall es más formal.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "rules",
          "rows": [
            { "key": "Shall I", "value": "Shall I open the window?", "highlights": ["Shall I"] },
            { "key": "Can I help", "value": "Can I help you?", "highlights": ["Can I help"] },
            { "key": "Would you like", "value": "Would you like some tea?", "highlights": ["Would you like"] }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pp-permission",
      "tag": "Permiso",
      "title": "Can / Could / May I",
      "lede": "Para pedir permiso, de lo más informal a lo más formal.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "rules",
          "rows": [
            { "key": "Can I (informal)", "value": "Can I sit here?", "highlights": ["Can I"] },
            { "key": "Could I (educado)", "value": "Could I borrow your pen?", "highlights": ["Could I"] },
            { "key": "May I (formal)", "value": "May I come in?", "highlights": ["May I"] }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tip": {
        "label": "Registro:",
        "body": "May I es lo más formal; Can I, lo más cotidiano. Could I queda bien casi siempre."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "pp-requests",
      "tag": "Pedir",
      "title": "Pedir favores",
      "lede": "Pedirle a otra persona que haga algo. Could you y Would you suenan educados.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "rules",
          "rows": [
            { "key": "Can you", "value": "Can you help me?", "highlights": ["Can you"] },
            { "key": "Could you", "value": "Could you repeat that?", "highlights": ["Could you"] },
            { "key": "Would you mind", "value": "Would you mind closing the door?", "highlights": ["Would you mind"] }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tip": {
        "label": "Ojo:",
        "body": "tras Would you mind va -ing: Would you mind waiting?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "pp-responses",
      "tag": "Responder",
      "title": "Aceptar y rechazar",
      "lede": "Cómo responder a propuestas, ofertas y peticiones de forma natural.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "contrast",
          "columns": [
            {
              "label": "Aceptar",
              "rule": "decir que sí",
              "examples": ["Sure! · Of course.", "That sounds great.", "Yes, please."]
            },
            {
              "label": "Rechazar",
              "rule": "decir que no con tacto",
              "examples": ["Sorry, I can't.", "Maybe another time.", "I'd love to, but..."]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pp-practice",
      "tag": "Práctica",
      "title": "Mini diálogo",
      "lede": "Así se encadenan propuesta, respuesta y plan en una conversación real.",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "pairs",
          "lines": [
            { "variant": "good", "text": "Why don't we go for coffee?", "note": "propuesta" },
            { "variant": "good", "text": "Sure, that sounds great!", "note": "aceptar" },
            { "variant": "good", "text": "Could you pick me up?", "note": "petición" },
            { "variant": "good", "text": "Of course, no problem.", "note": "aceptar el favor" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
